brown-forman & lt ; bfdb > to chang record date brown-forman inc said at the suggest of the american stock exchang it ha chang the record date for the 28 ct per share quarterli dividend on it class a and class b common stock that is payabl april one to march 20 from march 13 , to coincid with the record date for a three-for-two stock split declar februari 26. it said the record date for the dividend on it four pct cumul prefer stock ha also been chang to march 20 from march 13 .